metadata.name: COSMIC SAFARI COVER
metadata.description:
I give you the first edition in the Cosmic Safari Pages 1/1 collection. The cover of the graphic novel! 

Every Friday I will drop either an animated 1/1, A page 1/1 Auction  
or an edition piece. 

Holders of Cosmic Safari 1/1's are guaranteed all utilities listed on CosmicSafariComic.com including a signed copy of the hardcover graphic novel upon its release. (only eligible to those holding upon release of the book.) 

Welcome to the Cosmic Safari!
